textTemplates.name: tp_City
textTemplates.text: Select Id,Name, code__c from City_Master_Data__c where province_code__c = '{!edit_Province.selectedChoiceValues}'

textTemplates.name: tp_Kecamatan
textTemplates.text: Select Id, Name, code__c from District_Master_Data__c where city_code__c = '{!func_GetCity}'

textTemplates.name: tp_Kelurahan
textTemplates.text: Select Id, Name, code__c from Sub_District_Master_Data__c where district_code__c = '{!func_GetKecamatan}'

textTemplates.name: tp_ZipCode
textTemplates.text: Select Zip_Code__c from Sub_District_Master_Data__c where code__c = '{!func_GetKelurahan}'
